{"tid":366637,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"重光72周年 紀念二戰保衛香港犧牲軍人","createTime":"2017-08-20T07:35:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-20T10:44:38.000Z","uid":79563,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3732ed607251b91ace3f8e5e75d5326cd660aea8","tid":366637,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T07:35:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170820/57104349\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170820%2F57104349&d=DsmaqcTzu27K8cC6FG0AyHadZns4eLIrfSaUqUvMaEw%3D&h=b7e2f4df\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170820%2F57104349&h=a604a308\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170820/57104349</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170820/large/1503209040_520a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170820%2Flarge%2F1503209040_520a.jpg&h=240ddca4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港戰俘協會及皇家香港軍團協會，在香港大會堂紀念公園聯合舉辦重光72周年紀念儀式，紀念二次大戰中保衛香港犧牲的軍人及脱離日軍統治。有從軍多年的退役英軍表示已出席儀式多年，認為意義重大，讚揚當年犧牲的是無名英雄，值得被悼念。他指自己雖然當年沒參與戰役，但看到戰役發生亦感受深刻。<br />\n<br />\n英國駐港領事賀恩德、政府代表、美國駐港領事唐偉康、多名退役皇家英軍和退役二戰軍人亦有出席儀式，期間眾人默哀，並向花園中央，保存陣亡者名冊和刻上陣亡隊伍名字木匾的12邊形紀念龕獻花。  <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170820/large/1503209045_b1d8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170820%2Flarge%2F1503209045_b1d8.jpg&h=e647e484&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170820/large/1503209053_fcb3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170820%2Flarge%2F1503209053_fcb3.jpg&h=f8e59a04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.